            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I was able to mitigate this issue by doing any of the following:\n* setting `highlight = false` for tree-sitter\n* changing `api.nvim__redraw({ buf = self.bufnr, range = { ch[1], ch[4] }, flush = false })` in [highlight.lua](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/29011e4d4574c66d80ddaac01744bf693b4b0552/runtime/lua/vim/treesitter/highlighter.lua#L240) to `api.nvim__redraw({buf = bufnr, valid=true, flush=true})`, which makes me think tree-sitter might not be fully aware of additional virtualtext lines",
